      "writtenOn": "2020-03-24T13:33:54Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "suggestion: split these test cases into two groups - one with Algorithm specified, one with it omitted. Then you have one input (expectations) and one output, which makes the test function more likable.\n\nRationale: testing that we default to exact matching feels like a different concept than just testing exact matching.\n\nsuggestion: get rid of MakeExpectations - bake that into the test function/loop. Pass in just the label of the image in question.",
